note_en:
Orbit includes over 50 easy to use components and enables you to quickly construct clean and scalable applications.
       Import the following CSS file as an asset to your build.  Do not @import them into the style tag of your App.vue, as doing so will unecessarily pre-process them.
    &lt;template&gt; &lt;div id=&#34;app&#34;&gt; &lt;h1&gt;Orbit v2&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;o-button&gt;Button&lt;/o-button&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/template&gt;&lt;script&gt; // Components are imported individually as needed. // Note the object {} syntax. &#39;import OButton&#39; will not work. import { OButton } from &#39;@square/orbit/components/Button&#39;; export default { name: &#39;app&#39;, components: { OButton } }&lt;/script&gt;
